title: Photograph, "Chalice or Cup"
description: The drinking component of the object has the appearance of hammered metal, while the base shows raised elements, perhaps encrusted with gems. Dark shadows and bright highlights alternate in the depiction of of both object and background in the photograph.

tombstone.epitaph:
Photograph, "Chalice or Cup".
Gelatin silver print. Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-73.
